{
  "stem": "14897.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We later found out that he got very little from that package.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But at least he got enough to know that we were all right, because he was getting something from us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No letters were allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No visits were allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this life came to an end abruptly, again, when the war started between Germany and Russia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sloniam was overrun within two or three days by the Germans, as was the whole eastern part of Poland and a considerable part of Russia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father joined us very soon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was released from prison, oddly enough, by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And although it was not pre-arranged, my mother had left our location with various members of the Jewish community in Baranowicze, particularly with doctors.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he found a Jewish doctor, found out where we were, and walked to join us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A little funny story while he was walking-- two funny stories.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The first one, there was a movement, of course, of German troops.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now this is not the Gestapo or the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This is the Wehrmacht, the German military, moving deeper into Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my father is trudging on the side of the road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I have to tell you that although I was not considered to look Jewish, my father did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he, he just looked Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And here these German units are tr-- are walking by, marching by.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And one of them yells to my father in German, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And just by accident, that was my father's name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he was of course thinking of generic, for Jews, you know, like King Solomon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Also during that trip, he had to spend the night because he couldn't walk it in, in one day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there were wolves.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
